                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                        
   ╭────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮   
   │   Hive Help                                                                                                    │   
   │              ╭───────╮                                                                                         │   
   │  Keys   tmux │ Usage │ Features                                                                                │   
   │──────────────╯       ╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────│   
   │  Views                                                                                                         │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │  Hive has two main layouts:                                                                                    │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │    tab    Sidebar view — tree of projects and sessions with a live preview pane.                               │   
   │    g     Grid view    — compact cells showing all sessions in the current project.                             │   
   │    G     All-sessions grid — every session across all projects.                                                │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │  Navigation                                                                                                    │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │    ↑ / k        move up                                                                                        │   
   │    ↓ / j        move down                                                                                      │   
   │    [ / ]        jump to previous / next project                                                                │   
   │    space         toggle project collapse                                                                       │   
   │    ←  / →        collapse / expand project                                                                     │   
   │    tab          switch between sidebar and preview pane                                                        │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │  Projects & Sessions                                                                                           │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │    p    new project (choose directory)                                                                         │   
   │    n    new session in the current project                                                                     │   
   │    W    new worktree session (new git branch + directory)                                                      │   
   │    r    rename project or session                                                                              │   
   │    x    kill session                                                                                           │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │  Attaching                                                                                                     │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │  Press enter or a to attach to a session.                                                                      │   
   │                                                                                                                │   
   │ ←/→:switch tab  ↑↓/j/k:scroll  ?/esc:close                                                                     │   
   ╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯   
                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                        